@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
actor Customer
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "Order Service" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "VNPay Gateway" as VNPay

Customer -> FE: Proceed to Checkout
FE -> API: Validate Cart & Compute Total (incl. Shipping)
API -> DB: Check Inventory
DB --> API: Inventory OK
API --> FE: Return Checkout Details

Customer -> FE: Confirm Order & Select VNPay
FE -> API: Create Order (Status: Pending Payment)
API -> DB: Save Order
API -> VNPay: Generate Payment URL
VNPay --> API: Payment URL
API --> FE: Redirect to Payment URL
FE --> Customer: Show VNPay Portal

Customer -> VNPay: Enter Card/Bank Info & Pay
VNPay -> API: Webhook: Payment Success
API -> DB: Update Order Status (Paid)
API -> DB: Deduct Inventory
API --> VNPay: Acknowledge Webhook (200 OK)

VNPay --> FE: Redirect to Return URL (Success)
FE -> API: Fetch Order Status
API --> FE: Order is Paid
FE --> Customer: Display Order Success Page
@enduml
